description.plain:
Lud Foe is an up-and-coming rapper from Chicago, Illinois. He was co-signed by fellow Chicago rapper Lil Durk, who remixed his song “Cuttin Up”.

Lud Foe gained more exposure when “Cuttin Up Remix” was featured on Episode 26 of OVO Sound Radio.

description.plain: “My Life” is the intro to Lud Foe’s “#GetWellFoe” mixtape, released on March 23rd, 2017. The song covers what life was like growing up for Lud Foe on the west side of Chicago. Growing up without a father, Lud Foe had to mature at an early age and try to provide for his family at the same time, while only being a young teenager. The song and the entire mixtape is produced by longtime friend KidWond3r.
